The findings are based on available online resources and interpretations, which may not encompass the full spectrum of Jewish thought and historical context. Additionally, the diversity of Jewish beliefs and the evolution of Messianic expectations over time mean that this report may not capture all nuances. Further research, including primary historical texts and scholarly works, would provide a more comprehensive understanding.